### 1. Software Description

LanCuiZhiJian (揽萃知鉴) is an AI-powered intelligent text processing desktop application built on Tauri 2 (Windows platform), with the following features:

- **8 AI Service Providers**: Built-in DeepSeek, ChatGPT, Anthropic, Google Gemini, Qwen, Kimi, Doubao, Zhipu — 8 providers with 25 models; custom provider compatible with OpenAI API format
- **5-Stage AI Processing Pipeline**: Semantic Chunking → Information Extraction → Noise Filtering → Semantic Enhancement → Content Reconstruction, batch-parallel execution with per-stage fallback strategies
- **8-Strategy URL Intelligent Extraction**: Rust native HTTP (bypasses CORS) → WebView headless rendering → Third-party API → Browser fetch → Web Archive, 3-layer intelligent scheduling
- **Text Preprocessing Pipeline**: 7-step preprocessing (encoding fix / Unicode normalization / special character removal / whitespace normalization / 50-pattern boilerplate removal / line deduplication / structure preservation), compression ratio protection
- **Enterprise-Grade Request Optimization**: Circuit breaker / LRU cache / request deduplication / adaptive timeout / exponential backoff retry / concurrency control / provider health tracking
- **Three Input Methods**: URL extraction, text input (max 5,000 characters), file import (TXT/MD/DOCX/DOC/JSON/CSV/XML/HTML/LOG, max 10MB)
- **Multi-Format Export**: Markdown / Plain Text / Word document, save path selected via Tauri file dialog
- **Trilingual Internationalization**: Simplified Chinese / English / Japanese, ~662 translation keys; Light / Dark / System themes
- **Task Management**: 6 states / 4 priorities / background queue / checkpoint resume / auto-retry / batch operations
- **Dual-Source Updates**: GitHub / Gitee dual update sources

